title: FPL GW14 - LIVERPOOL TOP 4 AT RISK! - FPL Family (Fantasy Premier League Tips 2022/2023)
description:

Elsewhere, Lee laments a poor Liverpool performance, but another reasonably decent week in FPL. So what now for Salah? Is Lee going to hold for Leeds, or look to sell?
